no matter what Liberty Rail admits.

281
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:09,169
You are such a cold,
heartless son of a bitch.

282
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:10,964
And this isn't about your parents,

283
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:13,082
so back them
into whatever comer you want,

284
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,884
but when they refuse
to admit what they did,

285
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:17,566
you are not going to trial.

286
00:13:21,520 --> 00:13:23,204
Stay out of my case.

287
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:37,608
Something smells delicious.

288
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:41,401
I'm making us dinner,
but it won't be ready for a while.

289
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:45,800
