00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:56,688
- Looks French.
- Mmm-hmm.

308
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,684
So you let me go through
all that even though

309
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:01,689
you knew you were gonna
say yes the entire time?

310
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:02,642
Mmm-hmm.

311
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:05,004
Aren't you glad I did?

312
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:07,887
Yes, Jessica.

313
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:11,008
Yes, I am.

314
00:15:23,680 --> 00:15:24,727
Donna, what are you doing here?

315
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:27,645
