to accept that on his own.

330
00:15:55,680 --> 00:15:56,886
- Donna...
- Harvey,

331
00:15:57,040 --> 00:15:58,929
when are you gonna
let him be his own man?

332
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:00,889
His own man?
He's out of control.

333
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:03,008
