with his parents.

334
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:05,771
And you're out of control because
you can't separate yourself from him.

335
00:16:05,880 --> 00:16:07,325
Okay, you need to stay out of it.

336
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:09,408
