what it is you're talking about.

382
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:30,209
They are answering the phones
"Pearson Specter,"

383
00:18:30,320 --> 00:18:33,210
- not "Pearson Specter Litt."
- Louis...

384
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:34,970
You don't believe me?
Check it yourself.

385
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:36,491
I'm not harassing our support staff.

386
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:37,726
It's not harassment, God damn it!

387
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:38,966
- Louis!
- Jessica,

388
00:18:39,120 --> 00:18:42,647
it's like they've been specifically
instructed to leave my name off.

389
00:18:42,840 --> 00:18:43,807
Now you're just being paranoid.

390
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:45,445
I am not paranoid.
They're in lockstep.

391
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,608
I'm telling you, someone paid them off.

392
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:49,688
Louis, that's insane,

393
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:53,561
but if you want them to say your name,
I will get them to say your name.

394
00:19:01,360 --> 00:19:03,408
Jessica, what can I do for you?

395
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:05,761
You can explain to me
why you paid our reception staff

396
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,848
not to say Louis' name
when they answer the phone.

397
00:19:08,560 --> 00:19:10,324
- Who says I did that?
- They do.

398
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,044
God damn it.

399
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:14,766
I paid them good money to keep Louis
from finding out for at least a month.

400
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:16,126
He hasn't found out.

401
00:19:16,280 --> 00:19:18,248
It wasn't him who got them
to crack, it was me.

402
00:19:18,360 --> 00:19:20,044
Even still, I'm asking for a refund.

403
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,441
Jeff, I'm serious about this.

404
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:27,200
I know you're pissed about
how he got his name on the door,

405
00:19:27,360 --> 00:19:29,727
but I need you to bury the hatchet.

406
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:31,803
