- Why not?

407
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:33,809
Because every single time
I see his rat face,

408
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:35,160
I think about him blackmailing you,

409
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:37,806
and it makes me want to walk over to
him and rip his arms off his body.

410
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:41,242
And that little phone prank
was just my way

411
00:19:41,360 --> 00:19:44,409
of keeping myself
from doing something like that.

412
00:19:44,520 --> 00:19:47,330
I understand,
and I do appreciate it,

413
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:50,606
but I'm not asking you
to do it for him.

414
00:19:50,720 --> 00:19:52,324
I'm asking you to do it for me.

415
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:03,128
Mr. Ross.

416
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:04,765
All I can say about
your filing is that I think

417
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:06,809
you might have a career
writing fiction.

418
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:08,883
