my client into a big fat check.

422
00:20:14,680 --> 00:20:15,761
I'm sorry to be the one
to tell you this,

423
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:18,770
but a big fat check isn't
gonna get you out of this.

424
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:20,609
- Is that a fact?
- It sure as hell is,

425
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:23,929
because we both know that report
says you're responsible for this accident,

426
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:26,122
and we're not settling
anything without you admitting it.

427
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:28,208
And we're not admitting
something we didn't do.

428
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:32,001
What the hell is this?

429
00:20:32,120 --> 00:20:34,771
Well, you wanted the report.
Here it is.

430
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:36,763
