on our heat sensors,

433
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:42,001
and they passed every one.

434
00:20:44,600 --> 00:20:45,567
This is bullshit.

435
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:48,041
The only thing that's bullshit
is Joe Henderson.

436
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:51,448
He doesn't care about the accident.
All he's trying to do is shake us down,

437
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:54,171
exactly like he did at his last fourjobs.

438
00:20:57,720 --> 00:21:00,610
- What the hell is that?
- His last four lawsuits.

439
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:02,846
Did you think we wouldn't
find out about them

440
00:21:02,960 --> 00:21:04,644
just because the records
were sealed?

441
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:08,810
Mr. Ross, your client's been playing
the whistle-blower lottery for years.

442
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:11,685
He's never won before.
He's not going to win today.

443
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:25,164
You son of a bitch,
you tried to blow the whistle

444
00:21:25,320 --> 00:21:28,164
at every job you've ever had,
and now they know it!

445
00:21:29,040 --> 00:21:30,849
Keep your voice down.

446
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:34,723
Are you... No, I'll keep my voice down
when you stop bullshitting me.

447
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:36,888
Those claims were
supposed to be sealed.

448
00:21:37,080 --> 00:21:39,003
I don't care what they were
supposed to be.

449
00:21:39,120 --> 00:21:42,010
They found them, and you were
supposed to tell me about them.

450
00:21:42,120 --> 00:21:43,963
And what would you
have done if I did?

451
00:21:44,080 --> 00:21:45,161
I would've said what they said,

452
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:47,010
that you don't give a shit
about what they did!

453
00:21:47,120 --> 00:21:48,645
You're just looking to get rich.

454
00:21:48,760 --> 00:21:52,003
You think I would've risked my job
and everything that I have for nothing?

455
00:21:52,720 --> 00:21:53,607
Excuse me?

456
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:55,609
I said, I don't see you

457
00:21:55,720 --> 00:21:59,247
working out of the goodness
of your heart in your $1,000 suit.

458
00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:02,643
You have no idea
who I am or why I do things.

459
00:22:02,800 --> 00:22:05,724
And I told you, you don't have to be
concerned about my history

460
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:07,769
because what I'm telling you is true.

461
00:22:08,760 --> 00:22:10,444
Well, not according to this.

462
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:12,722
