gave us all the leverage

463
00:22:12,840 --> 00:22:14,888
and they say proves them innocent.

464
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:16,650
That report is bullshit,

465
00:22:16,760 --> 00:22:19,161
because I'm telling you,
those sensors didn't work,

466
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,970
